snippet.title: Cellyon: Boss Confrontation - Teaser 2020
snippet.description:
Cellyon: Boss Confrontation is a Co-Op Boss fighting game inspired by the best MMORPGs.

The game is scheduled to be released in early access at the end of 2020.


Full details on our Steam page !:  https://store.steampowered.com/app/802120/Cellyon_Boss_Confrontation/

Follow us on our social networks to avoid missing any news on Cellyon: Boss Confrontation.
